hazaaron khwaishein aisi is an indian film made by director sudhir mishra in 2003 but released in 2005 . set against the backdrop of the indian emergency , the movie tells the story of three young people in the 1970s , when india was undergoing massive social and political changes . the title is taken from a poem by urdu poet mirza ghalib . it went to 12 film festivals in 6 months including turkey , estonia , river to river ( florence ) , berlin , edinburgh , washington , goa , bite the mango ( bradford ) , commonwealth ( manchester ) , india ( los angeles ) , dallas , and pacific rim ( california ) .